    # Currency Exchange Rate System

A simple full-stack project developed with Node.js, Express, HTML, CSS and JavaScript.  
The application consumes a public external API to display real-time currency exchange rates.

## Project Overview

This project was created to practice the integration between a backend and a frontend using an external public API.

The backend was developed with Node.js and Express. It is responsible for consuming the external API and returning the exchange rate data to the frontend.

The frontend was developed with HTML, CSS and JavaScript. It allows the user to select a currency and dynamically displays the quotation information on the screen.

## Features

- Public API consumption
- Backend and frontend integration
- Dynamic data display
- Currency selection
- Exchange rate consultation
- Basic error handling
- Responsive and clean interface

## Technologies Used

### Backend

- Node.js
- Express
- Axios
- CORS

### Frontend

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript

### External API

- AwesomeAPI Currency API

