How to Run the Project
1. Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/Leonardo06TCLeo
2. Access the backend folder
cd api-cotacao-moedas/backend
3. Install dependencies
npm install
4. Start the backend server
node server.js

The backend will run at:

http://localhost:3000
5. Open the frontend

Open the file below using Live Server in Visual Studio Code:

frontend/index.html


Example response:

{
  "USDBRL": {
    "code": "USD",
